According to a report by Intel Market Research, the global Automotive Artificial Intelligence Market was valued at USD 36.70 billion in 2025 and is projected to grow from USD 47.40 billion in 2026 to USD 368.30 billion by 2034, registering a remarkable CAGR of 29.1% during the forecast period.
